    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the powerband. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive valve adjustment. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, while the atmospheric induction provides the signature metallic rasp enthusiasts crave. This is a mechanically sorted specimen that prioritizes analog feedback and chassis dynamics.",
