      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 Executive Sport Sedan in a striking Midnight Sapphire finish. This vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and shows the pride of ownership throughout. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss with only minor, unavoidable stone chips consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the premium parchment leather interior remains supple and free of tears or heavy bolster wear; it has been a strictly smoke-free environment. All onboard electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, navigation, and the premium 12-speaker sound system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has followed a strict synthetic oil change regimen every 5,000 miles. The tires were replaced last season and have significant tread remaining, ensuring a smooth and safe ride. The brakes are responsive with no pulsation, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. This listing includes a complete service history and two sets of keys. This is a reliable, sophisticated vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
